(33, 1, 'POM', '', '<p class="explain" style="font-size:16px;color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<b>POM is an acronym for the chemical name polyoxymethylene.</b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:Arial;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left">\r\n	It is generally\r\nreferred to as polyacetal or acetal resin. <span class="hps">The material has</span> <span class="hps">excellent overall\r\nperformance</span>: <span class="hps">mechanical</span> <span class="hps">properties,\r\nchemical properties</span>, <span class="hps">thermal properties are relatively</span> <span class="hps">balanced,</span> <span class="hps">coupled with superior</span> <span class="hps">process-ability</span>, to become <span class="hps">the leader in</span> <span class="hps">engineering plastics</span>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/prosperity/www/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150303/20150303165749_98858.png" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<span style="line-height:1.5;">-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The\r\nmaterial retains well balanced mechanical properties over extended use and a\r\nwide temperature range. These properties include tensile strength, elongation,\r\nand impact strength.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]-->-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Superior\r\ncreep resistance is exhibited over a wide temperature range for extended\r\nperiods under load.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]-->-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Exceptional\r\nfatigue resistance is possessed. No fatigue is exhibited in use under\r\nrepetitive stress and continuous vibration, and stable performance is\r\nmaintained.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]-->-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;High\r\nelastic modulus and superior elastic recovery are exhibited, in addition to\r\ncreep and fatigue resistance, making the material the material of choice by far\r\nfor springs.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]-->-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Amongst\r\nthermoplastics, the material has the most exceptional friction and wear\r\nproperties, and exhibits superior tribological properties over extended use. In\r\naddition, it is self-lubricating, and used widely in non-lubricated components.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]-->-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Besides\r\nhaving superior short-term thermal properties such as melting point and DTUL,\r\nunrivalled long-term durability is exhibited in hot air and hot water\r\nenvironments.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]-->-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Dimensional\r\nvariance as a result of water absorption is minimal, and for all intents and\r\npurposes does not present a problem.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]-->-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Other\r\nthan acids and chemicals with a strong oxidizing effect, excellent durability\r\nwith regards to inorganic chemicals and oils is shown.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]-->-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Possessing\r\nsuperior flowability and beautiful surface gloss, the material has excellent\r\nprocessability.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n	<!--[if !supportLists]-->-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A\r\nvariety of value-added processes are possible, including insert molding,\r\noutsert molding, cutting work, bonding, and printing.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<img src="/prosperity/www/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150303/20150303175700_43647.png" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left">\r\n	Mainly used in gears, bearings, screws and other\r\nmechanical parts etc\r\nfor the center application. In DVD player, Blu-ray Disc players and other AV equipment; printers,\r\ncopiers and other OA equipment; washing machines, refrigerators, shavers and\r\nother appliances; fuel tank cap, fuel pump, belts and other parts and supplies\r\nautomotive interior on auto parts. Also in terms of housing-related fields,\r\nsuch as window frames and shutters parts and the new game\r\nconsoles.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;"> \r\n	<table style="width:100%;" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="ke-zeroborder" bordercolor="#FFFFFF">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect1.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">Fuel pump modules</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect2.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">Music box parts</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect3.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">Sanitary equipment\r\nparts</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect4.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">Carrier components\r\n(reduction gear mechanisms)</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect5.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">Door lock side covers</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect6.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">Door lock actuators</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect7.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">Blind components</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect8.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">Mechanical components\r\nfor DVD-ROM drives</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', '', ''),
(33, 2, 'POM', '', '<p class="explain" style="font-size:16px;color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="explain" style="font-size:16px;color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	POM一般称为聚甲醛或甲醛树脂（acetal resin）\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	是化学名聚氧化亚甲基（polyoxymethylene）的简称。该材料具有优良的综合性能：机械性能、化学性能、耐热性能都比较均衡，再加上超群的成型加工性，使其成为当今工程塑料的佼佼者。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<img src="/prosperity/www/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150105/20150105164348_39867.png" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　长时间和较宽的温度范围内，能保持拉伸强度、拉伸率及冲击强度等各种机械特性的平衡。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　在较宽的温度范围内和长时间的载荷条件下，仍具有优良的耐蠕变特性。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　具有非常优良的耐疲劳特性，即使在重复应力和连继振动的条件下，仍能持续保持稳定的特性。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　具有高刚性及优良的弹性恢复性能，再加上良好的耐疲劳和耐蠕变性，是理想的弹簧材料。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　耐磨耗特为热塑性塑料之最，同时它还具有良好的润滑性。此外，它还具有自润滑特性，适用于无油润滑机械零部件。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　没有因吸水而发生尺寸变化现象，实际应用中基本没有问题。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　除强酸、强氧化剂的化学药品外，对于其它的无机化学药品及油类具有超群的耐久性。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　具有良好的成型流动性和表面美观、光泽特性，是成型性能非常优良的树脂。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　适用于嵌件模塑，金属嵌件上注塑及切削加工，熔接，印刷等二次加工。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">－　不仅熔点、热变形温度等短期热性能十分优良，而且在高温空气及高温热水中长期使用时的耐久性亦呈现出良好的性能</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<img src="/prosperity/www/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150105/20150105164445_37680.png" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;">主要以在齿轮、螺丝及轴承等机械零件方面的应用为中心。应用在DVD播放器、Blu-ray 光盘播放器等AV机器；打印机、复印机等OA机器；洗衣机、冰箱、剃须刀等家用电器；油箱盖、燃料油泵、安全带零部件以及汽车内饰用品等汽车零部件上。还应用在窗框及百叶窗零部件等住宅相关领域及最新的游戏机等方面。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="text pd-r40 l-h" style="font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:微軟正黑體;">\r\n	<span style="font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;line-height:1.5;"> \r\n	<table style="width:100%;" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="ke-zeroborder" bordercolor="#FFFFFF">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect1.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">燃料油泵模块</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect2.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">百音盒部件</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect3.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">卫生间用品部件</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect4.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">传动带部件</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect5.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">门锁侧盖</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect6.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">车门锁侧盖</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect7.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">百叶窗部件</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<img src="http://forester3.vizzhost.com/prosperity/20140924/images/effect8.png" alt="" /> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">DVD-ROM驱动</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style="color:#BF0000;font-family:微軟正黑體;">器的机械部件</span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', '', '');
